---

## [1.0.0] - 2025-10-28
### Added
- Initial release of **Brutalist Portfolio — Duong Phu Đông**
- Built with Next.js (App Router) and TypeScript
- Sections: Home, Education, Skills, Projects, Activity, Interests, Contact
- Deployed on Vercel at [https://brutalist-portfolio-dong.vercel.app](https://brutalist-portfolio-dong.vercel.app)

